  "content": "\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cd68b7190c3a0ec1\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere are some actually funny dark one-liners, stupid dad jokes, and short 恶搞 (prank) jokes:\n\n### Actually Funny Dark One-Liners\n\n*   I just got my doctor's test results, and I'm really upset about it. Turns out, I'm not gonna be a doctor.\n*   My grief counselor died. He was so good, I don't even care.\n*   You don't need a parachute to go skydiving. You need a parachute to go skydiving twice.\n*   I asked my phone, \"Siri, why am I still single?\" It activated the front camera.\n*   My senior relatives liked to tease me at weddings, saying things like, \"You'll be next!\" They stopped once I started doing the same to them at funerals.\n*   I just read that someone in New York gets stabbed every 52 seconds. Poor guy.\n*   The doctor gave me one year to live, so I shot him with my gun. The judge gave me 15 years. Problem solved.\n*   My husband told me to do whatever makes him happy. I'm going to miss him.\n*   I wasn't close to my dad when he died, which is lucky because he stepped on a landmine.\n*   My therapist said time heals all wounds, so I stabbed her.\n\n### Stupid Dad Jokes\n\n*   Why don't skeletons fight each other? They don't have the guts.\n*   What do you call cheese that isn't yours? Nacho cheese!\n*   I used to be a baker, but I couldn't make enough dough.\n*   I'm reading a book on anti-gravity. It's impossible to put down!\n*   Why couldn't the bicycle stand up by itself? Because it was two-tired.\n*   What did the pony say when she had a sore throat? I'm a little horse!\n*   My friend claims he glued himself to his autobiography. I don't believe him, but that's his story and he's sticking to it.\n*   What's brown and sticky? A stick.\n*   \"Dad, I'm hungry.\" \"Hi Hungry, I'm Dad.\"\n*   Did you hear about the kidnapping at the playground? They woke up.\n*   I used to be addicted to the hokey-pokey. But then I turned myself around.\n*   What did the grape say when it got stepped on? Nothing, it just let out a little wine.\n*   Why can't your nose be 12 inches long? Because then it would be a foot.\n*   What do you call a fake noodle? An impasta.\n\n### Short 恶搞 (Prank) Jokes that are Actually Funny\n\nThese are harmless pranks that usually get a laugh!\n\n*   **\"Updog\" Joke:** Say to someone, \"I'm thinking of having updog for lunch.\" They'll likely respond, \"What's up, dog?\"\n*   **\"Under Where\" Joke:** Ask someone, \"Whatcha eating under there?\" (Under where / underwear).\n*   **Say \"Roast\" 10 times:** Have someone say the word \"roast\" 10 times fast. Then ask them what you put in a toaster. (They'll likely say \"roast\" instead of \"bread\").\n*   **Plastic Wrap Doorway:** Secure clear plastic wrap at chest height across a frequently used doorway.\n*   **Fake Bugs/Snakes:** Place realistic-looking fake insects or snakes in unexpected places around the house or office.\n*   **Toothpaste Oreo:** Carefully remove the filling from an Oreo cookie and replace it with toothpaste.\n*   **Rubber Banded Keys:** Wrap multiple rubber bands around all the keys on someone's keychain, making it a \"rubber band cocoon.\"\n*   **Saltwater in Drinking Glass:** Dissolve a bit of salt in a glass of water and offer it to someone.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cd68b7190c3a0ec1\">>>",
